    <ul class="list-group mb-4">
        <li class="list-group-item">
            <strong>Seamless Server Listing:</strong> Add your server to the toplist effortlessly by logging in via Discord OAuth2.
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
            <strong>Free and Secure Access:</strong> No need for separate registration—Discord login ensures security for server owners and players alike.
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
            <strong>Visibility:</strong> Gain exposure to the growing OSRS community, with a chance to rank higher based on community engagement.
        </li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-warning">For Players</h3>
    <ul class="list-group mb-4">
        <li class="list-group-item">
