        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
            <strong>Ease of Voting:</strong> Support your favorite servers with a single click, directly impacting their position on the toplist.
        </li>
        <li class="list-group-item">
            <strong>Secure Experience:</strong> No personal information is stored by PlayZanaris beyond Discord username data, ensuring a safe browsing environment.
        </li>
    </ul>

